gGqE","ref":"Mark.9.33","text":"And he came to Capernaum: and being in the house he asked them, What was it that ye disputed among yourselves by the way?","year":32},{"id":"recEITLMlhiqAPHGM","ref":"Luke.4.23","text":"And he said unto them, Ye will surely say unto me this proverb, Physician, heal thyself: whatsoever we have heard done in Capernaum, do also here in thy country.","year":27}]}
